# @attation Please define a global system variable %%MISBUILD%% or
# 			$MISBUILD in you shell config or in your windows system
# 			settions which holding the path the path to the root folder of
# 			this build system.  Normaly the  path to set is the folder where
# 			this cnfig makefile stays.
#
#
